:: YukariIntro
The woman stopped, leaned over my back and took a sniff. I could feel the increased warmth from her as her cold hands clasped themselves on my shoulder.
A short sniff, probably around 5 seconds, yet it felt like an eternity as my heart rate sped up. 

She clasped her nose and walked backwards away from me. @@.yukari; You smell disgusting.@@

"Me?" I uttered, as she fanned herself while pinching her nose. 

@@.yukari;I doubt any Youkai would want to eat you.@@

"..." Knowing better, I kept silent. I wanted to know more about the situation I'm in, but that could wait. 

@@.yukari;Since you got two hands and legs, it would be a waste to just let you go.@@

She raised a hand and snapped her fingers. That same void that brought me into this room reappeared, \
and I swallowed into the murky abyss, with those eyes staring at me as my consciousness melted in the void. 

